INTRO TO NLP
Shehroze Khan (ccid: shehroze) and Afia Anjum (ccid: afia)

Place the assignment-3.py file in the directory which contains the directory "A3DataCleaned" with all of the train and test .txt files.

Run the program. It will generate 14 .txt files. The name of each file will specifiy the tagger type, either "hmm" or "brill," the data its trained on, 1 for Domain1, 2 for Domain2 and ELL for ELL, and the file it is tested on. These files will be generated in the same directory as the assignment-2.py file.

Furthermore, the program will also print to the console the accuracy scores of the taggers corresponding to the same filenames.

The intermediate files that are used to run the Stanford POS tagger output is provided in the Folder named Stanford.


====Commandline Commands for Stanford===

===running Domain1 and Domain2 files====
Train:
java -classpath stanford-postagger.jar edu.stanford.nlp.tagger.maxent.MaxentTagger -prop Domain1Trainprop.props -model Stanford1 -trainFile Domain1Trainprocessed.txt
java -classpath stanford-postagger.jar edu.stanford.nlp.tagger.maxent.MaxentTagger -prop Domain2Trainprop.props -model Stanford2 -trainFile Domain2Trainprocessed.txt

Test:
java -classpath stanford-postagger.jar edu.stanford.nlp.tagger.maxent.MaxentTagger -prop Stanford1.props -model Stanford1 -testFile Domain1Testprocessed.txt
java -classpath stanford-postagger.jar edu.stanford.nlp.tagger.maxent.MaxentTagger -prop Stanford2.props -model Stanford2 -testFile Domain2Testprocessed.txt
Opposite test:
java -classpath stanford-postagger.jar edu.stanford.nlp.tagger.maxent.MaxentTagger -prop Stanford1.props -model Stanford1 -testFile Domain2Testprocessed.txt
java -classpath stanford-postagger.jar edu.stanford.nlp.tagger.maxent.MaxentTagger -prop Stanford2.props -model Stanford2 -testFile Domain1Testprocessed.txt


Running models on the ELL

===Stanford on ELL====
==test==
java -classpath stanford-postagger.jar edu.stanford.nlp.tagger.maxent.MaxentTagger -prop Stanford1.props -model Stanford1 -testFile ELLTestProcessed.txt
java -classpath stanford-postagger.jar edu.stanford.nlp.tagger.maxent.MaxentTagger -prop Stanford2.props -model Stanford2 -testFile ELLTestProcessed.txt

Retraining taggers on ELLTrain.txt
train
java -classpath stanford-postagger.jar edu.stanford.nlp.tagger.maxent.MaxentTagger -prop Domain1Trainprop.props -model ELL -trainFile ELLTrainProcessed.txt

test
java -classpath stanford-postagger.jar edu.stanford.nlp.tagger.maxent.MaxentTagger -prop ELL.props -model ELL -testFile ELLTestProcessed.txt

